window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Creatures, conjurers, and...cosplay?</p> <p>Protect Sefu. On paper it looks simple.</p> <p>Only I have no idea who Sefu is, much less how to find him or her. And my magic’s not talking. But with demons on the hunt, and fiendish whispers of Sefu being some sort of ultimate weapon, failure could spell apocalypse. One of those demons happens to be an enemy I cast into the Pits, a former vampire lord whose twisted mind drips vengeance. Worse, he knows about my relationship with Detective Vega and her son. Meaning I have much more than Sefu to protect.</p> <p>In the Order’s absence, I’m scraping together what help I can. Let’s just say that with the hunt for Sefu tracking through a major sci-fi and fantasy convention, my new teammates and I will blend right in.</p> <p>That is until a shadowy conjurer threatens Epic Con and its thousands of costumed attendees.</p> <p>A conjurer whose name might be Sefu…</p> <p>Books in The Croftverse<br> </p> <p><b>Prof Croft Series</b></p> <p>Preq 0: Book of Souls</p> <p>Book 1: Demon Moon</p> <p>Book 2: Blood Deal</p> <p>Book 3: Purge City</p> <p>Book 4: Death Mage</p> <p>Book 5: Black Luck</p> <p>Book 6: Power Game</p> <p>*More to come*</p> <p><b>Blue Wolf Series</b></p> <p>Book 1: Blue Curse</p> <p>Book 2: Blue Shadow</p> <p>Book 3: Blue Howl</p> <p>* More to come *</p>"; 
